---
title: Caprese-Inspired Tarts with Stone Fruit Salad
description: Are you ready for a new take on the beloved Caprese salad? A puff pastry tart base is topped with basil mayo, oven-burst baby tomatoes and marinated fresh mozzarella. Served alongside is a fresh and fruity salad with sweet nectarines and balsamic vinaigrette.
